{"tid":588294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改街名變毛澤大道東？香港政協倡去殖民符號","createTime":"2018-03-11T06:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T06:27:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f35419cdd5f3eafb06b05194cec704b1583f38c","tid":588294,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180311/20328188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F20328188&d=wnrB4YlbdlhvLVZtTTAyVMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=de29cff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F20328188&h=752379a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180311/20328188</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n改街名變毛澤大道東？香港政協倡去殖民符號<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n每年北京兩會期間，都有唔少愛國紅人發表「偉論」，今年又點會例外？為咗配合阿爺去殖化「柯打」，有政協委員促使特區政府去掉同埋減少殖民政府留下嘅符號，仲話可以由香港嘅地名同道路名開始。「知己一聲拜拜遠去這都市，要靠偉大同志搞搞新意思」，唔少人噚日即刻將羅大佑同蔣志光嘅《皇后大道東》狂loop，同時亦「一呼百應」自發配合佘委員嘅愛國大業，提出好多精闢建議，其中「雜種道」就好多人like，阿爺唔知肯唔肯制？"},{"pid":"f6163a7fc64eebfa63bdffcf7537f895934526e0","tid":588294,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"大陸啲名好難記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923ed34f327e0a24bf1d916a487230532b20fb09","tid":588294,"uid":32619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iXwwtfS6jg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiXwwtfS6jg4&d=wnrB4YlbdlhvLVZtTTAyVMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6de17adb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iXwwtfS6jg4</a>"},{"pid":"5a6f246865d2727b799a41aa2ce867b5059e1cd0","tid":588294,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11